{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b1",
      "translation": "AIA is a trusted partner for our customers, enabling them to focus on financial security and family protection with peace of mind. Despite the far-reaching impact of the COVID-19"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b2",
      "translation": "pandemic, I am deeply grateful to our employees, agents and partners for their flexibility and dedication in adapting to new ways of working and ensuring uninterrupted support to our customers"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b3",
      "translation": "during this challenging period."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b5",
      "translation": "Since the onset of the pandemic, our business teams across the Group have responded swiftly and actively worked to mitigate the impact on our communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group has"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b6",
      "translation": "implemented a comprehensive range of measures, including financial support, provision of medical supplies, complimentary coverage, access to healthcare resources, streamlined service processes and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b7",
      "translation": "accelerated claims payments, which I am proud of. We continue to find every reason to pay claims, and during the year we paid out over USD 16 billion in insurance benefits and claims,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b8",
      "translation": "providing our customers with critical financial protection."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b9",
      "translation": "Although measures to contain the COVID-19 pandemic resulted in new business value declining to USD 2.765 billion, as restrictions on movement eased, sales momentum turned positive and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b10",
      "translation": "gathered very strong momentum in 2021, with new business value in the first two months growing 15% year-on-year. Our large and growing in-force portfolio generates high-quality and recurring"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b11",
      "translation": "income streams, driving a 5% increase in operating profit after tax in 2020, while free surplus generated during the period grew 7%. As at 31 December 2020, embedded value equity reached a record high of USD 67.2 billion, and the Group's local capital aggregation method coverage ratio stood at 374%, demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b12",
      "translation": "our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b13",
      "translation": "The Board recommends a final dividend for 2020 increased by 7.5% to HKD 100.30 per share. This reflects AIA's long-standing prudent, sustainable and progressive dividend policy, which enables the Group to"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b14",
      "translation": "capture future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b15",
      "translation": "AIA possesses several distinctive competitive advantages that set us apart in a highly competitive market. With decades of operations in Asia, we have an unparalleled platform in the region and hold"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b16",
      "translation": "leading positions in most of our markets. Our consistent and unwavering focus exclusively on Asia enables us to capture growth opportunities across the world's most attractive life insurance region. This focus,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b17",
      "translation": "combined with our leadership team's extensive experience in Asia and the quality of our workforce, has been a key driver of our strong performance."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b18",
      "translation": "Our unparalleled distribution strength enables direct customer engagement and delivery of high-quality professional advice to meet the substantial and growing long-term protection and savings needs of Asian consumers. Today, customers increasingly expect companies to address their needs in ways that are aligned with long-term sustainable development. AIA has a market-leading brand"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b19",
      "translation": "built on the purpose of helping people live healthier, longer, better lives."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b20",
      "translation": "We aim to position AIA as a global leader in technology application, enhancing connectivity, expanding scale and improving efficiency. Deeper insights from data analytics enable us to create unique and personalized customer experiences. Products and services tailored to and reflective of individual needs and lifestyles have transformed how people view life insurance,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b21",
      "translation": "establishing a strong foundation for building long-term relationships with our customers."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b22",
      "translation": "Although 2020 was an unprecedented year, I am more optimistic than ever about the prospects for Asia's life insurance industry and AIA's future. We continue to challenge ourselves and develop our strategic priorities to ensure we remain well-positioned to meet evolving customer expectations and financial needs. Our new corporate strategy builds on AIA's existing strengths and advances our transformation to deliver the best service to our customers in the years ahead."
    },
